Description: This package provides convenient access to a comprehensive collection of evapotranspiration datasets. 
  It offers researchers, scientists, and practitioners an easy way to retrieve valuable evapotranspiration data.
  The package includes clear documentation and instructions for downloading the datasets, making it seamless to 
  integrate into various research applications. With diverse evapotranspiration data available at different spatial 
  and temporal resolutions, users can tailor their data exploration to their specific research needs. 
  By facilitating access and utilization of evapotranspiration data, this package supports hydrological modeling, 
  climate studies, agricultural research, and other data-driven fields.
